            <title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Provides links to a <link linkend="de/d4d/namespace_modular_1_1_grid_list">GridList</link> either for filtering or as an action such as &apos;clear&apos;. This is removed from <link linkend="de/d4d/namespace_modular_1_1_grid_list">GridList</link> as it may go on pages which link to the gridlist but do not themselves have a <link linkend="de/d4d/namespace_modular_1_1_grid_list">GridList</link>. The <link linkend="de/d4d/namespace_modular_1_1_grid_list">GridList</link> maintains state so cannot be added to all pages which need these links.</para>

